title: Democrats Torpedo Bipartisan Talks With Take-It-Or-Leave-It Obamacare Plan
description: Democrats proposed a three-year extension of the enhanced Obamacare premium subsidies despite the measure's near-certain failure to secure the votes needed.
content:
Democrats on Thursday proposed a three-year extension of the soon-to-expire enhanced Obamacare premium subsidies despite the measure’s near-certain failure to secure the votes needed to pass.
